    "description": "<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Requirements: </strong>you must have mastered the <strong>Esper</strong> Class.</span></p></blockquote><p>While your <strong>Brainwave Clock</strong> is <strong>full</strong>, you may use an action to erase all of its sections. If you do, you may choose one option: you deal <strong>@DMG[20 physical]</strong> damage to every enemy that is present on the scene; <strong>or</strong> you deal <strong>@DMG[30 physical]</strong> damage to a single enemy you can see. This amount increases by 10 if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or by 20 if you are <strong>level 40 or higher.</strong></p>",
